names.alias: 57 kDa iron-sulfur cluster assembly factor for biotin synthase- and aconitase-like mitochondrial proteins
ISA1-ISA2-IBA57 mitochondrial iron-sulfur protein assembly complex

attributeList.attribute: Reductive coupling most probably occurs at the ISA1-ISA2 interface with IBA57 recruiting apo-target proteins to the complex.

Assembles [4Fe-4S] clusters from reductive coupling of two [2Fe-2S] clusters received from GLRX5 homodimers (CPX-6957). The [4Fe-4S] clusters can then be inserted into mitochondrial [4Fe-4S]-requiring proteins.
